<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>¡Compra Exitosa!</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-dark text-light d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center vh-100">

    <div class="card bg-secondary p-5 shadow-lg border-0 text-center" style="width: 35rem; border-radius: 12px;">
        <div class="mb-4">
            <div class="bg-success rounded-circle d-inline-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mb-3" style="width: 80px; height: 80px;">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-white" style="font-size: 3rem;"></i>
            </div>
            <h2 class="fw-bold text-white m-0">¡Gracias por tu compra, <%= cliente.nombre %>!</h2>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-light opacity-75 fs-5 mb-4">Tu pago se acreditó correctamente y ya estamos preparando tu pedido.</p>
        
        <div class="bg-dark p-3 rounded mb-4 text-start border border-secondary-subtle">
            <p class="m-0 small text-muted mb-1">Detalles de la operación:</p>
            <p class="m-0 fw-bold"><i class="fa-solid fa-receipt text-primary me-2"></i> Orden de Compra: #<%= id_venta %></p>
            <p class="m-0 fw-bold"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-invoice-dollar text-primary me-2"></i> ID Mercado Pago: <%= id_pago %></p>
        </div>

        <div class="d-grid gap-2">
            <a href="/tienda" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg fw-bold shadow-sm">
                Seguir comprando
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>